  &lt;p id="DAS7D8"&gt;We’re inching ever closer to a mid-cycle refresh for the PlayStation 5, as the PS5 Pro’s staggered preorder schedule is beginning. The $699.99 console is about to be available to preorder in the US at &lt;strong&gt;10AM ET / 7AM PT&lt;/strong&gt; through Sony’s &lt;a href="https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fbuy-consoles%2Fplaystation5-pro-console&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F24252575%2Fsony-ps5-pro-playstation-5-preorder-buy-price-release-date" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;PlayStation Direct storefront&lt;/a&gt;, so if you want to secure one ASAP, you’ll want to jump in line at Sony’s site (be sure to have your PlayStation Network login info handy).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id="rRD9pe"&gt;Also going up for preorder at the same time are &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/19/24249013/sony-playstation-ps5-pro-30th-anniversary-retro"&gt;Sony’s retro-styled 30th Anniversary&lt;/a&gt; PS5 Pro bundle (&lt;a href="https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fbuy-consoles%2Fplaystation5-pro-console-30th-anniversary-limited-edition-bundle%3Femcid%3Dot-ps-456950&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F24252575%2Fsony-ps5-pro-playstation-5-preorder-buy-price-release-date" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;$999.99&lt;/a&gt;), PS5 Digital Edition slim (&lt;a href="https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fbuy-consoles%2Fplaystation5-digital-edition-30th-anniversary-limited-edition-bundle-model-group-slim%3Femcid%3Dot-ps-456950&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F24252575%2Fsony-ps5-pro-playstation-5-preorder-buy-price-release-date" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;$499.99&lt;/a&gt;), PlayStation Portal (&lt;a href="https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fbuy-accessories%2Fplaystation-portal-remote-player-30th-anniversary-limited-edition%3Femcid%3Dot-ps-456950&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F24252575%2Fsony-ps5-pro-playstation-5-preorder-buy-price-release-date" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;$219.99&lt;/a&gt;), DualSense (&lt;a href="https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fbuy-accessories%2Fdualsense-wireless-controller-30th-anniversary-limited-edition%3Femcid%3Dot-ps-456950&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F24252575%